•	1,143sqm* office/warehouse unit

•	2 container roller doors
•	B-Double access to site  
•	Pylon signage to Robinson Road 
•	10 exclusive car parks on site  

For further information or to arrange an inspection time please contact marketing agents CBRE.

CBRE is pleased to offer for lease, 393 Bilsen Road, Geebung. 

This site is located within one of Brisbane’s most sought after northern industrial precincts, situated just 12km north of Brisbane’s CBD. Geebung has easy access to the Gateway Motorway, major arterial roads & airport link. Geebung is well serviced by both bus & train networks and is also just 15 minutes away from Brisbane Airport.

Features include:
+ 1,965sqm* total floor area
+ Semi clearspan warehouse 
+ 4,000sqm* Site area 
+ Office / showroom to be refurbished as required 
+ Multiple roller doors with on-grade & dock access 
+ Excellent truck turning and container set down areas
+ Ideal for warehouse distribution
+ Competitive rental 

*Approx.

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact CBRE agent.
